f:["$","p",null,{"style":"$7:props:children:props:children:1:props:style","children":"The key to deck-integrated outdoor kitchens is structural reinforcement (countertops and appliances are heavy), proper gas line routing, and weatherproof cabinetry rated for Virginia's freeze-thaw cycles. Granite and quartzite countertops handle temperature swings; soapstone is gaining popularity for its heat resistance near grills."}]
