13:["$","p",null,{"style":"$7:props:children:props:children:1:props:style","children":"The most popular configuration in our projects is marine-grade stainless steel cable with powder-coated black aluminum posts. This combination resists Virginia's humidity and requires zero maintenance beyond occasional cleaning."}]
